<hr>
<p><strong>In short:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>Induction</strong>: Build proof step-by-step.</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Contradiction</strong>: Prove by showing false assumption fails.=
</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Recursion</strong>: Define sequences/functions in terms of thems=
elves.</p></li>
</ul>
